news.title: CIDCO to allow conversion of residential leasehold plots to freehold
news.para: Maharashtra government approved a plan. This plan allows owners of residential plots allotted by CIDCO to convert their leasehold properties to freehold. CIDCO formed a committee to manage applications. The scheme applies to various plot allotments.

news.title: YEIDA to hold draw for residential plot scheme in Sector 18 on July 11
news.para: YEIDA is set to conduct a draw of lots for its Sector 18 residential plot scheme, featuring 276 plots, after receiving over 54,000 applications. The draw, supervised by retired High Court judges for transparency, will be broadcast live.

news.title: Bhubaneswar development body lets housing society cut power, water over dues
news.para: In a first for Odisha, the Bhubaneswar Development Authority has empowered an association of allottees to disconnect essential services to residents who fail to pay monthly maintenance fees. The order, citing the Odisha Apartment Act of 2023, addresses the issue of wilful non-payment by some flat owners, promoting shared responsibility within apartment complexes.
